Package: scSeuratBuilder
Type: Package
Title: Intelligent Seurat Object Builder with Strict Metadata Validation
Version: 2.2.1
Date: 2026-03-18
Author: xiaoqqjun
Maintainer: xiaoqqjun <xiaoqqjun@sina.com>
Description: Intelligent pipeline for building Seurat objects with mandatory metadata validation. Supports three data structures: subfolder-per-sample, direct files, and merged objects. Integrated geneSync support for gene name synchronization. Includes 10X triplet file validation and per-sample processing with resumability.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports:
    Seurat,
    Matrix,
    data.table,
    readr,
    readxl,
    magrittr,
    geneSync,
    hdf5r
Depends:
    R (>= 4.0.0)
URL: https://github.com/xiaoqqjun/scSeuratBuilder
BugReports: https://github.com/xiaoqqjun/scSeuratBuilder/issues
